ces with office space in room 132 and an equipment storage maintenance and preparation area in b17 in the basement level of the mitchell building all enquiries regarding the operation and management of the facility should be directed to sara cina stanford university school of earth sciences 397 panama mall ca 94305 2210 mitchell building 101 tel 650 723 2544 2012 stanford university related resources employment opportunities hartley conference center health and safety computing resources room resources how can we help maps & directions stanfordwho office of the registrar contact us connect to earth sciences facebook itunes u twitter youtube
